message.body: hi. how are you?
zoloft is kicking in. i having excessive yawning and swallowing....
Oh I know that feeling, like a sleepy cat. I'm ok, feeling too busy
pete feels as bad today as he did when i took him to the er 4 months ago. :(
Oh no...what are you guys going to do?
i dunno. he's got someone rx he's going to try.
i am so smiley...
Haha, soon you will be perky too!
pete has been prescribed a strong antipyschotic. i am very opposed to him taking it.
What is it? What are the side effects?
ambilify. i just don't like that it's the first thing this guy wants to do.
Right, can you get a second opinion?9
yes. i left a message with my mom's psychiatrist. hoping he will advise.
Good, that is scary. Did he say why Pete is regressing?
pete was so out of it. he didn't remember anything he said. i regret not going.
That's awful. I'm sorry, it seems like it must be really bad if he is so out of it four months later
i don't know. thanks. how you you? i've been thinking of you on a horse.

Haha, I took lessons when I was younger, but it is kind of funny. I'm a little concerned, yesterday yellow liquid started leaking from my nose. I think it's related to the vertigo. On my way to doctors
maybe you're an alien?
That was my first guess, or that my brain is falling out
cld be both
According to the Internet it's cerebral spinal fluid or sinus pollups
i love the internet. everything is so serious. it's probably just alien juice.
No one even offered that suggestion, I don't trust the Internet anymore
me neither. i emailed you about this drug pete was prescribed.
is there any time we can meet before my trip? or a phone date? missing you.
Do you work tonight? Or Sunday?
free sunday.
I will find out tonight, but I think Ella is going on a fishing trip for Girl Scouts on Sunday, I will let you know for sure, but maybe we can meet up for a bit
sounds nice.
